SUMMARY:Spring Tea (CAPACITY REACHED)
DESCRIPTION:UPDATE: REGISTRATION HAS REACHED CAPACITY.\n\nJoin us on Saturday\, April 18th\, for Spring Tea at the Baynard House from 1:00pm to 3:00pm. This is a free event. Donations appreciated. RSVP required. The Baynard House is located at 208 W. Lake Ave.\, Auburndale\, FL 33823.\n\n\n\nThere will be tea and desserts.\n\n\n\nFor more information or to RSVP\, please call Auburndale Parks and Recreation at (863) 965-5545.
URL:https://auburndalefl.com/event/spring-tea-rsvp-required/
LOCATION:Baynard House\, 208 W Lake Ave\, Auburndale\, FL\, 33823\, United States
CATEGORIES:City Events
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://auburndalefl.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/Spring-Tea.png
END:VEVENT
