SUMMARY:City Commission Meeting
DESCRIPTION:A City Commission Meeting will be held on Monday\, April 20\, 2026. The meeting will be held at City Hall in the Commission Room starting at 7:00 PM. \nThe agenda will be posted 48 hours prior to this meeting on our Agendas & Minutes page. \nPublic Notices can be found on our Public Notices page. \nIn compliance with the Americans with Disabilities Act (ADA)\, anyone who needs a special accommodation for this Meeting should contact the City Clerk’s Office at (863) 968-5133 at least 48 hours in advance of this Meeting.
URL:https://auburndalefl.com/event/commission-meeting/
LOCATION:Auburndale City Hall\, 1 Bobby Green Plaza\, Auburndale\, FL 33823\, Auburndale\, FL\, 33823\, United States
CATEGORIES:Public Meetings
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://auburndalefl.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/City-Seal-Website-7-22.png
